---
import RealestateLayout from '../../layouts/RealestateLayout.astro';
import CtaButton from '../../components/CtaButton.astro';
import NewsletterSignup from '../../components/NewsletterSignup.astro';
---

<RealestateLayout
  title="Sell Your Home in the GTA | Cory Wong, Real Estate Agent | Trustwell Realty"
  description="Thinking about selling in Toronto, Markham, or Richmond Hill? Cory Wong offers pricing strategy, MLS listing, and offer negotiation. Get a free home valuation."
  canonicalPath="/sell"
>
  <section class="page-hero">
    <div class="container">
      <h1>Sell Your Home in the GTA</h1>
      <p class="page-hero__subtitle">
        Pricing your home correctly, presenting it well, and negotiating offers are what
        determine your result. Cory brings a clear process to each of those steps.
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="content-section">
    <div class="container">
      <h2>What Cory Provides</h2>
      <div class="services-intro">
        <p>
          Sellers in the GTA are competing against other listings. How your home is priced,
          how it looks online, and how offers are handled all affect your outcome.
        </p>
        <p>Cory's seller services include:</p>
        <ul class="services-list">
          <li>Comparative market analysis to determine the right list price</li>
          <li>Preparation guidance: what to fix, what to skip, how to present</li>
          <li>Professional photography and MLS listing</li>
          <li>Marketing across digital channels</li>
          <li>Offer review and negotiation</li>
          <li>Coordination with your lawyer through closing</li>
        </ul>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="pricing-section">
    <div class="container">
      <h2>Pricing Strategy</h2>
      <div class="pricing-content">
        <p>Pricing is the most important decision you make before you list.</p>
        <p>
          Price too high and buyers skip your listing. Price too low and you leave money on
          the table. The right price reflects current market conditions, not last year's data
          or a neighbour's number.
        </p>
        <p>
          Cory prepares a comparative market analysis (CMA) using recent sales of comparable
          homes in your area. The CMA shows what buyers have paid for similar properties and
          where your home fits in the current range.
        </p>
        <p>
          In Toronto, Markham, and Richmond Hill, pricing strategy varies by neighbourhood and
          market conditions. Some situations support a hold-back offer strategy, where you list
          at a price designed to generate multiple offers. Others call for straightforward
          pricing. Cory will recommend the approach based on current data.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="process-section">
    <div class="container">
      <h2>The GTA Listing Process</h2>
      <div class="process-steps">
        <div class="step">
          <span class="step__number">1</span>
          <h3>Listing Consultation</h3>
          <p>Cory visits your home, walks through the property, and prepares the CMA. You'll come away from the conversation with a realistic price range and a clear picture of what to do before you list.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="step">
          <span class="step__number">2</span>
          <h3>Preparation</h3>
          <p>Not every improvement adds value. Cory will identify which repairs and updates matter to buyers and which ones to skip. The goal is to present the home well without spending more than you'll recover.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="step">
          <span class="step__number">3</span>
          <h3>Photography and Marketing</h3>
          <p>Professional photography is standard. The listing description, photos, and floor plan shape how buyers perceive your property before they visit. Cory's writing background means your listing will be accurate and readable.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="step">
          <span class="step__number">4</span>
          <h3>On Market</h3>
          <p>Your listing goes live on MLS and syndicates across major real estate portals. Showings are coordinated through a lockbox or scheduled directly.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="step">
          <span class="step__number">5</span>
          <h3>Offers</h3>
          <p>In competitive situations, multiple offers arrive on offer night. In slower markets, offers come in over time. Cory walks you through each offer, explains the terms, and negotiates on your behalf. The final decision is always yours.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="step">
          <span class="step__number">6</span>
          <h3>Accepted Offer Through Closing</h3>
          <p>Once you accept, conditions are fulfilled, deposits confirmed, and your lawyer prepares for closing. Cory stays engaged through the process.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="lead-form-section" id="valuation">
    <div class="container">
      <h2>Find Out What Your Home Is Worth</h2>
      <p class="lead-form-section__subtitle">Get a professional assessment of your property's current market value.</p>
      <form class="lead-form" id="seller-form" data-form-type="seller">
        <div class="form-row">
          <div class="form-field">
            <label for="seller-name">Name</label>
            <input type="text" id="seller-name" name="name" required autocomplete="name" />
          </div>
          <div class="form-field">
            <label for="seller-email">Email</label>
            <input type="email" id="seller-email" name="email" required autocomplete="email" />
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="form-field">
          <label for="seller-address">Property Address</label>
          <input type="text" id="seller-address" name="address" required placeholder="e.g., 123 Main Street, Markham, ON" />
        </div>
        <div class="form-field">
          <label for="seller-timeline">Timeline</label>
          <select id="seller-timeline" name="timeline">
            <option value="">When are you looking to sell?</option>
            <option value="asap">As soon as possible</option>
            <option value="1-3months">1-3 months</option>
            <option value="3-6months">3-6 months</option>
            <option value="6-12months">6-12 months</option>
            <option value="exploring">Just curious about my home's value</option>
          </select>
        </div>
        <div class="form-field">
          <label for="seller-notes">Anything else about your property?</label>
          <textarea id="seller-notes" name="notes" rows="3" placeholder="e.g., recent renovations, property type, number of bedrooms"></textarea>
        </div>
        <button type="submit" class="form-submit">Get a Free Home Valuation</button>
        <p class="form-status" id="seller-form-status" aria-live="polite"></p>
      </form>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="cta-banner">
    <div class="container">
      <h2>Want to Talk Through Your Situation First?</h2>
      <p>Book a free consultation to discuss your options and timeline.</p>
      <CtaButton href="/contact" label="Book a Consultation" variant="primary" />
    </div>
  </section>

  <NewsletterSignup heading="Get the GTA Market Report Each Month" />
</RealestateLayout>

<script>
  const form = document.getElementById('seller-form') as HTMLFormElement;
  const status = document.getElementById('seller-form-status') as HTMLElement;

  form?.addEventListener('submit', async (e) => {
    e.preventDefault();
    status.textContent = 'Sending...';
    status.className = 'form-status';

    const data = Object.fromEntries(new FormData(form));

    try {
      const res = await fetch('/api/lead', {
        method: 'POST',
        headers: { 'Content-Type': 'application/json' },
        body: JSON.stringify({ ...data, type: 'seller' }),
      });

      if (res.ok) {
        status.textContent = 'Thank you! I\'ll be in touch with your valuation.';
        status.classList.add('form-status--success');
        form.reset();
      } else {
        throw new Error('Failed');
      }
    } catch {
      status.textContent = 'Something went wrong. Please email directly or try again.';
      status.classList.add('form-status--error');
    }
  });
</script>

<style>
  .page-hero {
    padding: var(--space-2xl) 0 var(--space-xl);
    text-align: center;
  }

  .page-hero h1 {
    font-size: clamp(1.75rem, 4vw, 2.5rem);
    font-weight: 700;
    letter-spacing: -0.02em;
    margin-bottom: var(--space-md);
  }

  .page-hero__subtitle {
    font-size: 1.125rem;
    color: var(--color-text-muted);
    max-width: 34rem;
    margin: 0 auto;
    line-height: 1.6;
  }

  .content-section {
    padding: var(--space-xl) 0;
  }

  .content-section h2 {
    font-size: 1.5rem;
    font-weight: 600;
    margin-bottom: var(--space-lg);
    text-align: center;
  }

  .services-intro {
    max-width: 36rem;
    margin: 0 auto;
  }

  .services-intro p {
    font-size: 0.9375rem;
    color: var(--color-text-muted);
    line-height: 1.7;
    margin-bottom: var(--space-md);
  }

  .services-list {
    list-style: none;
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: var(--space-sm);
    margin-bottom: var(--space-md);
  }

  .services-list li {
    font-size: 0.9375rem;
    color: var(--color-text-muted);
    line-height: 1.6;
    padding-left: 1.5rem;
    position: relative;
  }

  .services-list li::before {
    content: '';
    position: absolute;
    left: 0;
    top: 0.5rem;
    width: 8px;
    height: 8px;
    background: var(--color-accent);
    border-radius: 50%;
  }

  .pricing-section {
    padding: var(--space-xl) 0;
    background: #f5f5f4;
  }

  .pricing-section h2 {
    font-size: 1.5rem;
    font-weight: 600;
    margin-bottom: var(--space-lg);
    text-align: center;
  }

  .pricing-content {
    max-width: 36rem;
    margin: 0 auto;
  }

  .pricing-content p {
    font-size: 0.9375rem;
    color: var(--color-text-muted);
    line-height: 1.7;
    margin-bottom: var(--space-md);
  }

  .process-section {
    padding: var(--space-xl) 0;
  }

  .process-section h2 {
    font-size: 1.5rem;
    font-weight: 600;
    margin-bottom: var(--space-lg);
    text-align: center;
  }

  .process-steps {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: var(--space-lg);
    max-width: 36rem;
    margin: 0 auto;
  }

  .step {
    position: relative;
    padding-left: 3.5rem;
  }

  .step__number {
    position: absolute;
    left: 0;
    top: 0;
    width: 2.5rem;
    height: 2.5rem;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    background: var(--color-accent);
    color: #fff;
    border-radius: 50%;
    font-weight: 700;
    font-size: 0.875rem;
  }

  .step h3 {
    font-size: 1.0625rem;
    font-weight: 600;
    margin-bottom: var(--space-xs);
  }

  .step p {
    font-size: 0.9375rem;
    color: var(--color-text-muted);
    line-height: 1.6;
  }

  .lead-form-section {
    padding: var(--space-xl) 0;
    background: #f5f5f4;
  }

  .lead-form-section h2 {
    font-size: 1.5rem;
    font-weight: 600;
    text-align: center;
    margin-bottom: var(--space-xs);
  }

  .lead-form-section__subtitle {
    text-align: center;
    color: var(--color-text-muted);
    margin-bottom: var(--space-lg);
  }

  .lead-form {
    max-width: 32rem;
    margin: 0 auto;
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: var(--space-md);
  }

  .form-row {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
    gap: var(--space-md);
  }

  .form-field {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: var(--space-xs);
  }

  .form-field label {
    font-size: 0.875rem;
    font-weight: 500;
  }

  .form-field input,
  .form-field select,
  .form-field textarea {
    padding: 0.625rem 0.75rem;
    border: 1px solid var(--color-border);
    border-radius: 6px;
    font-size: 0.9375rem;
    font-family: var(--font-sans);
    background: var(--color-surface);
    transition: border-color 0.15s ease;
  }

  .form-field input:focus,
  .form-field select:focus,
  .form-field textarea:focus {
    outline: none;
    border-color: var(--color-accent);
    box-shadow: 0 0 0 3px rgba(15, 118, 110, 0.1);
  }

  .form-submit {
    padding: 0.75rem 1.75rem;
    border-radius: 6px;
    font-weight: 600;
    font-size: 0.9375rem;
    background: var(--color-accent);
    color: #ffffff;
    border: none;
    cursor: pointer;
    transition: background-color 0.15s ease;
  }

  .form-submit:hover {
    background: var(--color-accent-hover);
  }

  .form-status {
    text-align: center;
    font-size: 0.875rem;
    min-height: 1.25rem;
  }

  .form-status--success {
    color: var(--color-accent);
  }

  .form-status--error {
    color: #dc2626;
  }

  .cta-banner {
    padding: var(--space-xl) 0;
    text-align: center;
  }

  .cta-banner h2 {
    font-size: 1.5rem;
    font-weight: 600;
    margin-bottom: var(--space-sm);
  }

  .cta-banner p {
    color: var(--color-text-muted);
    margin-bottom: var(--space-lg);
  }

  @media (max-width: 640px) {
    .form-row {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
    }
  }
</style>
